{
  "texts": [
    "This plan should have lesson objective, lesson activities, assessment, and teacher role.\"",
    "Based on these prompts, 18 lesson plans were generated.",
    "Since both ChatGPT and Gemini responded complete lesson plans, none of the outputs were excluded from the analysis.",
    "\"Regenerate\" function to generate a different response for the same prompts were not used for any prompt in this study.",
    "In order words, the first responses of the chatbots for each prompt were included in the data analysis process."
  ]
}